# Alpaca Paper Trading Credentials
# ─────────────────────────────────
# 1. Sign in at https://app.alpaca.markets
# 2. Switch to "Paper Trading" in the top-right navigation
# 3. Go to: Overview → API Keys → Generate New Key
# 4. Paste the Key ID and Secret Key below, then rename this file to .env

ALPACA_API_KEY=your_paper_api_key_here
ALPACA_API_SECRET=your_paper_api_secret_here

# Notes
# ─────
# • NEVER commit a .env file containing real secrets to version control.
#   Add .env to your .gitignore.
# • Options paper-trading must be enabled on your account:
#   Paper Trading → Account → Options Trading → Enable
# • The paper trading base URL is set automatically via TradingClient(paper=True).
#   You do not need to set ALPACA_BASE_URL here.
